# Tender Notice: Coolant Heater Kit
### Request for Proposal
#### The Government of Canada, Department of National Defence
#### Solicitation Number: W8486-239044/A
#### Reference Number: cb-4700-37969617
#### Tendering Authority: Deborah Moldowan, (819) 939-0832, Deborah.Moldowan@forces.gc.ca

**Summary**

The Department of National Defence is seeking proposals for the supply of a Coolant Heater Kit. The items are required to be delivered to both CFSD Montreal and CFSD Edmonton.

**Item Requirements**
1. GSIN: 2990, NSN: 2990-21-912-9955, COOLANT HEATER KIT
	* Part No.: PA3501, NCAGE: 36718
	* Quantity: 40
	* Unit of Issue: KT
	* Delivery Location: CFSD Montreal
2. GSIN: 2990, NSN: 2990-21-912-9955, COOLANT HEATER KIT
	* Part No.: PA3501, NCAGE: 36718
	* Quantity: 10
	* Unit of Issue: KT
	* Delivery Location: CFSD Edmonton

**Proposal Rules**
* The Crown retains the right to negotiate with suppliers on any procurement.
* Documents may be submitted in either official language of Canada (English or French).
* Bidders proposing an Equivalent or a Substitute Product must provide the brand name and model, and/or Part Number and the NCAGE they are offering.

**Contractual Terms**
* The expected contract duration is 160 days after contract award.
* Payment terms will be outlined in the contract.

**Trade Agreements**
* This tender is open to Canadian suppliers under the Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA).

**Procurement Details**
* Unspsc: 26101100 - Electric alternating current AC motors
* Regions of opportunity: World
* Regions of delivery: Edmonton
* Regions of opportunity/ delivery: Montreal

**Bidder Inquiries**
Any bid-related questions should be submitted to Deborah Moldowan via email at Deborah.Moldowan@forces.gc.ca.

### Attachments
To obtain the detailed tender notice, please visit: https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/4700/w8486-239044-rfq-eng.pdf (English) or https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/web
